Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you sea cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally we found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These are pretty serious \Nwounds, Luffy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Sabo anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo went home. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the boss monkey from Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the mountain bandit - Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why but I'm registered \Nas their foster parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand by and watch someone \Ntry to take my boys' lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if I'm not their real parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just let you go if you back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll have \Nto resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Ace?! \NDon't try to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam is a real villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a guy that a kid like you can beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--L-Let me fight, too!\N--No, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You all, why don't you \Ntake Luffy and go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility \Nfor bringing Ace home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,--Y-Yes, ma'am!\N--Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Come home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you overestimate your \Nability, you'll only get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the strong and the \Ncowardly survive in wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The brave always die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a dead man! The fire \Nis all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen all of the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's hot! It's hot!\N--There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion left a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going \Non but this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look, there is a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This path leads up to the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get away by following it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go before the fire returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:41.77,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,How awful they are to burn\Nthe area and the residents there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.07,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:48.85,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,how did you know the situation in such \Nan outlying country in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.88,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Is there something special \Nabout this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is an example of how \Nthe world will be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There can be no happiness in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nwhere the undesirables are thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I will change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in a country like \Nthis, there are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who are willing to \Nfight for freedom, come aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.40,Sign,,0,0,275,,{\blur0.3\fad(250,500)\fs77\bord2.3\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(205,250,\1a&H00&)\t(2230,2275,\1a&HFF&)}Goa Kingdom, Royal Palace
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.40,Sign,,0,0,275,,{\blur0.3\fad(250,500)\fs77\bord0\4a&HFF&}Goa Kingdom, Royal Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.31,Sign,,0,0,275,,{\blur0.3\fad(250,525)\fs77\bord2.3\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(205,250,\1a&H00&)\t(1615,1660,\1a&HFF&)}High Town
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.31,Sign,,0,0,275,,{\blur0.3\fad(250,525)\fs77\bord0\4a&HFF&}High Town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they find Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just called in the military. \NThey'll find him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Sabo is giving us \Na hard time, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this town really safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the fire will \Nengulf the town any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to enter High Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even allow a bug \Nto enter - nobles only!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Boss!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace and Dadan didn't return \Nfrom the burning Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, wait, Luffy. You're not \Nrecovered - where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go and look for Ace and Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seriously wounded. You \Nhave to rest nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of troops in Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to take care of the mess after the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just burned junk \Nthat they're throing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but survivors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill you if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Sabo is worrying about us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.52,Sign,,0,0,266,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs77\bord2.3\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}The former site of Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.52,Sign,,0,0,266,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs77\bord0\4a&HFF&}The former site of Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great view!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pain in the butt \Nto clean up this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we find a survivor, we're \Nto shoot them on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't as many dead \Nbodies as I thought there'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a big fire. It could've \Nburned out the bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that the \Nfire might get to this side of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that Bluejam's \Nship was on fire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to know that \Nthose villains got burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! it's a nice day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is a lovely morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with this game of tag, okay boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you \Nrun, you can't get away, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All the police and troops \Nhave a picture of you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never get out of High Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or even out of this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, change your uniforms and \Nstart working here as guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have our duties...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing that a nobleman can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the approval of your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, you must barricade \Nyourself in your room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and educate yourself in your role as a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, I can make things \Nhappen just by giving the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can take care of \Nyou or those two easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't you mend your ways \Nand study hard like Stelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...study so that you can make your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who brought you into the world, happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that will make you happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'm here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dependable, Stelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Let me buy you some luxurious clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for the ceremony the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There, we'll see the \NCelestial Dragon in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check your homework tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that you died in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are okay, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I'll put you guys in \Ndanger if I try to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is like a birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can stand living in \Nthis country filled with stale air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shift is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be sleeping on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. By the way, how \Nare things in the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony is just a day away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crazy. People are going \Nwild getting ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime \Nthing but I got to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy and I will be the only \Ntwo in this house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see the Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All the citizens will be \Nat the harbor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be such a pain to stand guard there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,compared with this baby-sitting gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The day of the World Noble \Nfrom the Grand Line's visit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Goa Kingdom has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A lavish ceremony is prepared \Nfor the arrival of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, \Nring, ring... Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is A-team on the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Celestial Dragon's ship \Nwill arrive in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that. It's all quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll continue to stand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! There is a ship leaving port!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--Is it a fishing boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come back here! Don't get \Nin the way of the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child! There's a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A child? I wonder which family he's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible! The \Nguard is looking after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice day! It's \Nperfect for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! That's mine! Somebody \Nstole my fish boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! He has a black flag on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he think that he's a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! A kid can't just become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where is he heading?\N--He's disrupting the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Government's ship will arrive soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, come back here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The scariest fate for me is to \Nlose myself in this country and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,turn into someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Sabo on that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Government's ship is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die if I crash into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. He's turning away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the commoners are welcoming us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so blessed that \Nit's rare to even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that a real \NCelestial Dragon is on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like a fish boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice to be captain \Nof a ship like that someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The fishing boat has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace and Dadan return to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As everyone is rejoicing \Nover their safe return,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they learn of the tragedy \Nthat struck Sabo at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizing with sympathy \Nwhat Sabo had tried to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and Ace are befallen \Nby regret and grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Take Care of Him for Me!\NA Letter From a Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
