Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.01,0:23:47.08,Title Card - Top,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\bord0\4a&HFF&}Take Care of Him for Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:47.08,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\bord3.3\c&H000000&}A Letter From a Brother!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.01,0:23:47.08,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\bord0\4a&HFF&}A Letter From a Brother!
